RACE.FOOTNOTES: ON THE EDGE was settled early on the inside, made a three wide move on the turn and came four wide into the lane, continued that move and went on even terms for the lead by the furlong marker and slowly edged clear to prove best, driving. MIGHTY MINION was reserved early, four wide on the turn and angled in nearing the quarter pole and had no rally. THE MAN TO SEE was four wide into the first turn, tracked the pace four to three wide and tired. BROBRO CORMAN vied for the lead on the inside and gave way at the five sixteenths.
